/a><div class="bio">举办过 255 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description">知乎发起的在线嘉宾讨论，详情请点击：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/20886632" data-editable="true" data-title="什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与" class="">什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与</a>？<br>圆桌页面：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable" data-editable="true" data-title="活动">活动列表</a></p></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/topic/20673515" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='t$t$20673515'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9ae59149544e02b569f8cdb0da115a12_l.jpg" alt="腾讯研究院 S-Tech 工作室" class="avatar d50"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/topic/20673515" class="name" data-hovercard='t$t$20673515'>腾讯研究院 S-Tech 工作室</a><div class="bio">举办过 1 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description">「 S-Tech 」即「 Society &amp; Technology 」，意为「科技与社会」 ，旨在连接现代科技与社会人文，关注互联网时代人们真实的生存状态。<br>研究项目：<br>社交网络斋戒；网络游戏研究；群体研究；VR心潮；社群研究；互联网X音乐。</p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/zhang-xin-49-20" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$zhang-xin-49-20'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f3b45f7e687a25ca058320137dbd4297_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="张昕"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/shuziwannian/zhang-xin-49-20/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/zhang-xin-49-20" data-hovercard='p$t$zhang-xin-49-20'>张昕</a><span class="icon icon-badge-id-an icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者 · 已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">北京大学心理与认知科学学院 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 副教授</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/li-jia-41-60-79" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$li-jia-41-60-79'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bea63864e45b481be8e8a61f8cc6947e_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="李佳"></img></a><div class="content"><a class="name author-link" href="/people/li-jia-41-60-79" data-hovercard='p$t$li-jia-41-60-79'>李佳</a><div class="bio">盘古智库老龄社会研究中心副主任，研究员</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/laufei" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$laufei'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4d724df77f35071492643c4a5af2cced_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="刘飞"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/shuziwannian/laufei/answers" class="answers text-muted">1 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/laufei" data-hovercard='p$t$laufei'>刘飞</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span><div class="bio">你所见的，都是错的。</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/kyoninth" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$kyoninth'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-452a1fe26d88488a8ea85753340f9d0d_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="花开杏仁核"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/shuziwannian/kyoninth/answers" class="answers text-muted">1 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/kyoninth" data-hovercard='p$t$kyoninth'>花开杏仁核</a><div class="bio">腾讯游戏 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 用户研究</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/mi-mi-57-24" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$mi-mi-57-24'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/02d65187a5b2caabcf9e7a60d677749b_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="米米"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/shuziwannian/mi-mi-57-24/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/mi-mi-57-24" data-hovercard='p$t$mi-mi-57-24'>米米</a><div class="bio">老年学研究 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 项目主任</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/echo-20-31-41" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$echo-20-31-41'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2d166c5d42acfc6c4488d2eb37d2c43c_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="小 k"></img></a><div class="content"><a class="name author-link" href="/people/echo-20-31-41" data-hovercard='p$t$echo-20-31-41'>小 k</a><div class="bio">腾讯研究院S-Tech工作室 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 研究员</div></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module participants"><div class="module-header"><h3>热门回答者</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items-fulid"><li class="item"><a href="/people/costan" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$costan'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d39c2509fe531b3791c0302b11816eb_l.jpg" alt="设计师李大锤" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/whatawonder" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$whatawonder'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/a1bc1d6566cc8f7151232c893600a138_l.jpg" alt="皆存疑" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/org/appso" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$appso'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a409bf782b7c37ab7430b2126af7eff5_l.jpg" alt="AppSo" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/sentimental_animal" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$sentimental_animal'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-96747798067fce8684336cf495e18f2c_l.jpg" alt="李米" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/patrick-zhang-3" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$patrick-zhang-3'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b26db6dfd40a4bc4d6dbef6e14f7d319_l.jpg" alt="Patrick Zhang" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/org/jing-shi-xin-li-da-xue-tang" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$jing-shi-xin-li-da-xue-tang'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6efac062d385f2bbc70faedb52b2c531_l.jpg" alt="京师心理大学堂" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/org/you-yan-she-47" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$you-yan-she-47'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2a9c6ed72cf475d25431350bbaf2283a_l.jpg" alt="游研社" class="avatar d50"></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="module"><div 